Class CcddDbVerificationHandler.TableIssue

  • java.lang.Object
    • CCDD.CcddDbVerificationHandler.TableIssue
  • Enclosing class:
    CcddDbVerificationHandler

    private class CcddDbVerificationHandler.TableIssue
extends java.lang.Object
    Table issue class. An instance is created for each issue found in a data or internal table, and contains the information needed to identify and correct the issue

      • TableIssue

           int column,
           java.lang.String data,
           java.lang.String[] rowData,
           CcddClassesDataTable.TableInformation tableInfo)
        Table issue class constructor
        Parameters:
        issue - description of the issue
        action - action to be taken to correct the issue
        command - PostgreSQL command to correct the issue; null if this is not a change to a table cell value
        row - row index for the update
        column - column index for the update; -1 if the update does not affect a specific column
        data - cell value; null if a specific cell isn't updated
        rowData - array of cell values for a table row; null if a row is to be deleted or the update does not affect an entire row
        tableInfo - reference to the table information
